{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I came across "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"!https://www.gatsbyjs.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GatsbyJS"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and found it intriguing. So I gave it a try. I have been wanting to learn more about "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"!https://graphql.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GraphQL"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for a while now. What better way to do so than to build a project with it? And that's it. That's why I built this blog with a combination of "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://reactjs.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ReacJS"}]},{"type":"text","value":", "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"!https://www.gatsbyjs.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GatsbyJS"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"!https://graphql.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GraphQL"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I am planning to use it to write about things that I am doing that might be of interest to or maybe could help someone else."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Be sure to checkout my "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"!https://github.com/justmejulian"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" to see what I am up to."}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"path":"/why","title":"A Blog?","date":"05.02.2019"}}},"pageContext":{}}